	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vir clarissime, mitto duos libellos, quos hic curavi imprimendos; tu fratribus eos communicato.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vos, qui magna estis doctrina et prudentia, magnos libros saepe editis; ego, vir pusillus, his scilicet libellis ludo et meum papam celebro.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cras iturus sum <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernam</placeName>; nam satis diu d[ominum] doc[torem] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20206" cert="high">Gribaldum</persName> expectavi nec possum amplius expectare, et sumptus et ratio negotiorum vetat.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Itaque si advenerit, dicito illi me <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernae</placeName> futurum et illic aliquandiu expectaturum, et ut secum advehat nepotem meum.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Utinam <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernam</placeName> mitteretis eas literas commendaticias,<note type="margin">a.R.: ...</note> quas coram dixi me desiderare, nempe ad dominos <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l41" cert="high">Bernates</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Inde profecturus sum ad videndos fratres <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Genevenses</placeName> et mox redibo ad vos, ut spero.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale et salve cum tota ecclesia et schola.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rogate pro me.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileae</placeName>, 25. iulii 1551.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p3375" cert="high">Vergerius</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">H[enrico] Bullingero</persName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
